data.name: title
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Text for the the title header of the site settings panel

data.name: nameLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Label on the Site Settings Panel 'Name' text box

data.name: descriptionLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Label on the Site Settings Panel 'Description' text box

data.name: privacyLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Label on the Site Settings Panel 'Privacy' drop-down

data.name: classificationLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Label on the Site Settings Panel 'Business classification' drop-down

data.name: saveButton
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Caption on the Site Settings Panel 'Save' button

data.name: closeButton
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Caption on the Site Settings Panel 'Close' button

data.name: privacyOptionPrivate
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] 'Private' Option text on the Site Settings Panel 'Privacy' drop-down

data.name: privacyOptionPublic
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] 'Public' Option text on the Site Settings Panel 'Privacy' drop-down

data.name: classicSiteSettingsHelpText
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Help text for the site settings panel where {0} is the classicSiteSettingsLinkText string formatted as a link.

data.name: classicSiteSettingsLinkText
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Text for the link taking the user to classic site settings. Used within the classicSiteSettingsHelpText string.

data.name: usageGuidelinesLinkText
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Link text that opens the group usage guidelines for the tenant. Group is a noun in this context.

data.name: deleteGroupLinkText
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Link text that opens a confirmation dialog to delete the current Group.

data.name: deleteGroupConfirmationDialogTitle
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Title of the confirmation dialog for deleting groups.

data.name: deleteGroupConfirmationDialogText
data.value: You are about to delete the '{0}' group. This will delete all '{0}' resources including the site, files, conversations, calendar, etc. Please backup any files or other content before proceeding. Do you want to continue?
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Descriptive help text for the delete group confirmation dialog. Placeholder {0} will be replaced with the Group's name.

data.name: deleteGroupConfirmationDialogCheckbox
data.value: Yes, delete this group and all its associated resources.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Text for the checkbox in the group deletion dialog that confirms the deletion and enables the Delete button.

data.name: deleteGroupConfirmationDialogButtonDelete
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Text for the 'Delete' button within the group deletion dialog. This button will start the Group deletion and dismiss the dialog.

data.name: changeImageButton
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Caption for the 'Change' button below the Group Image that launches a file browser so user can choose a new image.

data.name: removeImageButton
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-SPPage] Caption for the 'Remove' button below the Group Image that removes the newly chosen image.
